= MouseTracker =

== Features ==

* Tracks mouse using sound (pan for x coordenate, frequency for y coordenate)
* Daemon can be controled via d-bus interface and uses d-bus activation
* Writen in python
* Uses gstreamer for sound output
* uses gtk, gdk and pyatspi for capturing mouse events
* Stores preferences in json format


== requirements ==

* pygtk 2.0
* python gstreamer bindings (pygst) 0.10
* pyatspi
* dbus-python
* python >= 2.4 and simplejson module or python >= 2.6


